name: Carvers of the Runic Engine
description: There are Rootmason carvings all over the heirlooms of the Carvers of the Runic Engine. Why? How? They're also known for their adept handling of dune surfers. Now consorting and aligning themselves with the Gibbun leadership, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
